'''Brot-rib''' was an edible delicacy made from a [[brot]]. Three opportunistic [[Squib/Legends|Squibs]] trading material to [[Killik/Legends|Killiks]] during the [[Swarm War]] asked [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] and [[Princess/Legends|Princess]] [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa Solo]] to transport crates of brot-[[Rib/Legends|rib]], in return for assistance finding their daughter [[Jaina Solo Fel|Jaina Solo]] in the [[Chiss/Legends|Chiss]]-Killik war zone.

==Appearances==
*''[[Dark Nest I: The Joiner King]]'' {{1stm}}
*''[[Dark Nest III: The Swarm War]]'' {{Mo}}

